{"tid":1875664,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"屌你老母，聯署去各國叫佢地唔好無條件援助支國啦","createTime":"2020-02-12T02:23:11.000Z","updateTime":"2020-02-12T18:07:24.000Z","uid":173852,"like":2,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"c6daf4a6856cb725b2e1644e7af143af3703190c","tid":1875664,"uid":173852,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-12T02:23:11.000Z","msg":"1.垃圾國家 平時日日果頭屌人小日本依頭屌人美帝 <br />\n好似全世界逼害緊你咁<br />\n<br />\n2.好啦依家出事啦 又扮哂死狗又要死雞撐飯蓋<br />\n結果又係依邊肯幫支國？佢日日屌既小日本同美帝<br />\n而件事過左後你估支國識多謝你咩？又咪反轉豬肚就是屎<br />\n共產黨係點 過左咁多年你知我知單眼佬都知啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n3.老老柒柒，如果無實質人權、體制既讓步（承諾都咪信，對共狗就係要一分一毫都同佢計清楚），唔白紙黑字簽份協議，你幫支國就係養隻狗黎咬自己<br />\n<br />\n膚淺既人道理由係依度根本唔適用，共黨果種垃圾處理方式本身就係靠害。佢如果唔肯真係做d野出黎，我地更加唔應該比籍口佢綁架人民黎拎著數"},{"pid":"df353687df6b79f6beb8053d85e183fd74cf5eaf","tid":1875664,"uid":173852,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-12T02:25:47.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"e60afe2e351102fb33ba74bd0cd87ced4f8c581a","tid":1875664,"uid":173852,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-12T02:34:25.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"41ac2506e9f03c93ab62557e1ae676c67bd248be","tid":1875664,"uid":210778,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-12T02:48:53.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"01cecd7b79c642b12f47665b3ee0154f19362d0e","tid":1875664,"uid":173852,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-12T03:59:33.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"cd72a736291148419f0f9af63aba4637068a2bb9","tid":1875664,"uid":90457,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-12T04:09:24.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a960246f6fd86b9957ad9f869d15971380f43fb8","tid":1875664,"uid":173852,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-12T08:54:05.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"684c668f2c163699bdf5cffb2d2004efeb0010c4","tid":1875664,"uid":173852,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime